Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.58,0:53:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}我不需要. 丽莎.布热南不是我的孩子.{\r}\NI don't want them. Lisa Brennan is not my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.55,0:53:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}法庭不这么认为.{\r}\NThe courts disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.21,0:53:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}她跟很多人乱搞, 孩子肯定不是我的. 至少不太可能是我的.{\r}\NChris-Ann is a lunatic. It's impossible. At the very least, improbable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.51,0:53:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}你知道做个亲子鉴定{\r}\NYou knew going into this
