Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.19,0:53:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}因此120万人都有可能是那个孩子的爸爸.{\r}\NThat's 1.2 million people that could be the father of that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.61,0:53:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}而且我不是孩子的爸爸.{\r}\NAnd it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.19,0:54:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}你说服我也没用, 关键是你得签这个名.{\r}\NYou don't need to convince me. But you do need to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.82,0:54:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}布热南小姐要求你付赡养费.{\r}\NMiss Brennan is entitled to your child support
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.70,0:54:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}不管你签不签这个字都一样.{\r}\Nregardless of whether you sign it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.79,0:54:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}你真的要放弃你的探视...{\r}\NDo you really want to give up the rights to see your...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.12,0:54:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}她的女儿的权利?{\r}\NTo see her child in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.92,0:54:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}我没时间.{\r}\NI don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.38,0:54:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}现在不行.{\r}\NNot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.50,0:54:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}史蒂夫, 身为人父, 我拜托你签一下字.{\r}\NSteven, as a father, I implore you to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.59,0:54:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}不管你认不认丽莎是你女儿.{\r}\NRegardless of whether you think Lisa is your daughter or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.47,0:54:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}签字没有风险.{\r}\NThere's no risk in signing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.01,0:54:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}不签, 你倒是有可能后悔.{\r}\NOnly the regret if you don't.
