Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.90,0:55:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}没错, 丹尼尔没有股份.{\r}\NYes. Daniel gets nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.99,0:55:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}没有股份?{\r}\NNothing?
