Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.12,0:55:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}我想过了, 丹尼尔没有股份.{\r}\NI have thought about it. Daniel gets nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.25,0:55:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}明白, 先生.{\r}\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.42,0:55:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}事情已经很明显了...{\r}\NIt's noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.96,0:55:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}什么?{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.71,0:55:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}随便一个初级工程师就能取代他.{\r}\NAny low grade technician could do his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.46,0:55:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}我白养了他很多年了. 不能感情用事.{\r}\NI've been feeding him for years. It's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.51,0:55:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}去你的感情用事, 史蒂夫. 他是你兄弟耶.{\r}\NDon't give me that bullshit, Steve. Of course it's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.97,0:55:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}他做现在的事都很吃力.{\r}\NHe can barely do his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.26,0:55:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}如果我们给丹尼尔股份,{\r}\NIf we give Daniel preferred stock,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.56,0:55:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}那些让比他强10倍的工程师情何以堪.{\r}\Nsome engineer with 10 times his talent gets nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.48,0:55:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}然后, 你猜怎么着?{\r}\NThen what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.64,0:55:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}我们现在就把原则定好, 行吗?{\r}\NThen we just draw this line right here, right now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.77,0:56:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}所以你在说些什么呢? 管理之道, 还是...{\r}\NSo you, what are you talking about? Management, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.94,0:56:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}管理层和工程师.{\r}\NManagement and engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.32,0:56:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}是的. 这意味着...{\r}\NYeah, this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.40,0:56:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}我真的了解, 麦克.{\r}\NI know what it means, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.94,0:56:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}谢谢.{\r}\NThanks.
