Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.17,0:56:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}和克里斯.艾斯品诺撒将不会{\r}\Nand Chris Espinosa will not
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.04,0:56:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&}得到{\r}\Nbe receiving
